DISCIPLINARY CASES

2012-2073. Disciplinary Counsel v. Oberholtzer.

On order to show cause. Mattheuw William Oberholtzer, Attorney Registration No. 0041239, is found in contempt for failure to comply with the court’s September 4, 2013 order. The previously imposed stay of his 12-month suspension is revoked, and he is suspended from the practice of law in Ohio.
